Well, it seems God has allowed Jesus to step things up a bit, now  they 
have formed more then just the one line in the darkness going into the  light, 
sure hope you guys can hear this one, because I and several other people  
are hearing the same thing,  "Operation good faith, get into the  lines"  It 
sounds like a conglomerate of people singing the words in a beat  like form.  
sf
